title: Mexico Oil Shipment Reaches Cuba, Increasing Tensions With US
description: A tanker carrying between 85,000 and 90,000 barrels of oil arrived in Havana from Mexico amid growing tensions with the US over the shipments after the fall of Venezuela’s ousted President Nicolás Maduro last week.
